  "detailed_description": "<strong>PLAY HOW YOU WANT:</strong>  There are no classes or restrictions.  You want to wield a two-handed axe and wear cloth armor?  Go for it!<br><br><strong>MULTIPLAYER:</strong>  Smaller scale instanced multiplayer currently supporting only a handful of players per instance.<br><br><strong>RANDOM ITEM GENERATOR:</strong>  Weapons and armor that drop have a chance to apply numerous stats.  There are hundreds of combinations!<br><br><strong>SKILL UP:</strong>  There are dozens of skills from long blades to cooking.  Level these just by doing them!<br><br><strong>EXPLORE:</strong>  Explore the land and find dungeons and other secrets!<br><br><strong>DROP ITEMS ON DEATH:</strong>   The name is Dura Vita after all.  Your inventory loot is dropped but can be recovered.  Also a possible weapon or armor piece equipped can drop too.",
